(Three LEFT JOINs)
SELECT *
FROM A

LEFT JOIN B
ON A.id = B.id

LEFT JOIN C
ON B.cid = C.cid

LEFT JOIN D
ON C.did = D.did;

Think of it as:

T1 = A LEFT JOIN B

T2 = T1 LEFT JOIN C

Result = T2 LEFT JOIN D

